Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:04.54,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}紧握决意抵在左胸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:09.33,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}劈裂「愚行之螺旋」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.88,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}翱翔于苍穹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:18.22,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自由之翼
